<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <BaseHead
            title="Privacy Policy | Digs Construction"
            description="Digs Construction values your privacy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit our website."
            keywords="Privacy Policy, Digs Construction, data protection, user privacy, website privacy, information security"
            url="https://digs.construction/privacy"
        />
    </head>
    <body>
        <SkipMain />
        <header>
            <NavMainDark />            
        </header>
        <main id="main">
            <section id="top">
                <div class="padding-xl-top">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="wrapper">
                            <h1 class="title-section text-underline">Privacy Policy</h1>
                        </div>

                        <!-- 1. INTRODUCTION -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">1. Introduction</h2>
                        <p>
                            Digs Construction ("Company," "we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy and is committed to 
                            protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard 
                            your information when you visit our website (<a href="https://digs.construction">https://digs.construction</a>).
                        </p>

                        <!-- 2. INFORMATION WE COLLECT -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">2. Information We Collect</h2>
                        <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and company name when you submit a contact form.</li>
                            <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, and operating system to enhance website performance.</li>
                            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent on the site, and other analytics to improve user experience.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <!-- 3. HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                        <p>We use the collected data for the following purposes:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>To respond to your inquiries and provide customer support.</li>
                            <li>To improve our website, services, and user experience.</li>
                            <li>To ensure website security and prevent fraud.</li>
                            <li>To comply with legal and regulatory obligations.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <!-- 4. DATA SHARING & THIRD PARTIES -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">4. Data Sharing & Third Parties</h2>
                        <p>We do not sell or rent your personal information. However, we may share data with:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>**Service Providers:** Third-party vendors assisting in website analytics, hosting, and security.</li>
                            <li>**Legal Authorities:** If required to comply with laws, regulations, or legal requests.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <!-- 5. COOKIES & TRACKING TECHNOLOGIES -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">5. Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>
                        <p>
                            We use cookies to improve functionality and enhance user experience. You can manage cookie 
                            preferences through your browser settings. Learn more in our <a href="/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a>.
                        </p>

                        <!-- 6. DATA SECURITY -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">6. Data Security</h2>
                        <p>
                            We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data. However, no method of online 
                            transmission is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
                        </p>

                        <!-- 7. YOUR RIGHTS & CHOICES -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">7. Your Rights & Choices</h2>
                        <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Request access to your personal data.</li>
                            <li>Request corrections or deletion of your data.</li>
                            <li>Opt-out of marketing communications.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>To exercise your rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@digs.construction">contact@digs.construction</a>.</p>

                        <!-- 8. THIRD-PARTY LINKS -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">8. Third-Party Links</h2>
                        <p>
                            Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy 
                            policies of external sites. Please review their policies before providing any personal information.
                        </p>

                        <!-- 9. CHILDREN'S PRIVACY -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
                        <p>
                            Our website is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal 
                            data from children. If you believe we have, please contact us to remove it.
                        </p>

                        <!-- 10. POLICY UPDATES -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">10. Policy Updates</h2>
                        <p>
                            We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated 
                            revision date.
                        </p>

                        <!-- 11. CONTACT INFORMATION -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">11. Contact Information</h2>
                        <p>
                            If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <strong>Digs Construction</strong><br/>
                            Los Alamos, NM<br/>
                            (505) 663-6115<br/>
                            <a href="mailto:contact@digs.construction">contact@digs.construction</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>   
        </main>
        <Footer />
